WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.710
Hello, my name is Brandon, and I'm going

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:04.950
to tell you about a visitation I

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:06.950
had from the Lord. I don't

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:09.830
know if it was a dream

00:00:09.830 --> 00:00:09.840
or

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:13.190
an out-of-body experience; all I

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.189
know is that it changed my life

00:00:16.199 --> 00:00:18.950
forever. I'm just going to get

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.189
right into it and tell

00:00:21.199 --> 00:00:24.230
you what happened. It was a normal

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:28.109
night on July

00:00:28.109 --> 00:00:28.119
6,

00:00:28.119 --> 00:00:31.509
2014.

00:00:31.519 --> 00:00:34.069
I went to bed,

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:35.069
and

00:00:35.079 --> 00:00:38.389
what

00:00:38.399 --> 00:00:40.310
happened

00:00:40.310 --> 00:00:40.320
next

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:41.590
is

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:44.389
mind-blowing.

00:00:44.399 --> 00:00:46.310
I want

00:00:46.310 --> 00:00:46.320
you

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:48.310
to give me a little bit of your

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:50.709
time.

00:00:50.719 --> 00:00:52.470
What I am about to tell

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:55.430
you will change your life forever if you

00:00:55.440 --> 00:00:57.510
let it and meditate on what

00:00:57.510 --> 00:00:57.520
is

00:00:57.520 --> 00:01:00.189
about to

00:01:00.199 --> 00:01:03.590
happen. Earth as we know it,

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:06.630
everything we see on

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:08.870
a day-to-day basis, is about to

00:01:08.870 --> 00:01:08.880
change—from

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:12.230
the

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:14.310
biggest thing to the smallest thing.

00:01:14.320 --> 00:01:17.670
This is what happened:

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:20.789
I went to bed, and

00:01:20.789 --> 00:01:20.799
suddenly

00:01:20.799 --> 00:01:23.910
I was taken out of my body.

00:01:23.910 --> 00:01:23.920
In

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:27.429
a dream, you don't smell,

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:30.230
taste, or feel

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:32.630
heat the way

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:34.710
I did. Suddenly, I was standing

00:01:34.720 --> 00:01:37.990
at a courthouse, and I looked over to my

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:41.270
right; Jesus was standing right there next to

00:01:41.270 --> 00:01:41.280
me. He was

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:44.630
looking at me. I

00:01:44.630 --> 00:01:44.640
looked

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:47.270
around,

00:01:47.270 --> 00:01:47.280
and

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.670
there

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:52.469
were

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:55.910
people rioting

00:01:55.910 --> 00:01:55.920
and

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:59.749
burning cars. People

00:01:59.749 --> 00:01:59.759
were

00:01:59.759 --> 00:02:01.109
destroying things, throwing

00:02:01.109 --> 00:02:01.119
things,

00:02:01.119 --> 00:02:04.389
acting crazy. I

00:02:04.389 --> 00:02:04.399
was

00:02:04.399 --> 00:02:07.510
taken aback by what I

00:02:07.510 --> 00:02:07.520
saw

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:09.749
because I could

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:12.630
smell the smoke and the fires. I could see the

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:16.550
courthouse on fire

00:02:16.550 --> 00:02:16.560
and

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:20.630
mass chaos everywhere. A lady

00:02:20.630 --> 00:02:20.640
ran

00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:23.190
up to me, and I asked, "What is

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:25.670
going on?"She said, "Don't you know?

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:28.750
Didn't you see? All the Christians are

00:02:28.760 --> 00:02:32.150
gone. All the Christians are gone."I

00:02:32.150 --> 00:02:32.160
asked,

00:02:32.160 --> 00:02:35.270
"Where did they go? What

00:02:35.270 --> 00:02:35.280
happened?"She

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.110
said the aliens came

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:39.830
and took them.

00:02:39.830 --> 00:02:39.840
Suddenly,

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.229
I looked

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:45.670
up, and there

00:02:45.670 --> 00:02:45.680
were

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:48.309
lightning strikes all over the

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:51.430
sky. It looked like a major storm, but

00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:53.350
there was no rain.

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:55.509
I could see lightning

00:02:55.509 --> 00:02:55.519
in

00:02:55.519 --> 00:02:58.150
the clouds;

00:02:58.150 --> 00:02:58.160
they

00:02:58.160 --> 00:03:00.150
were

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:02.869
active, like an

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:05.509
electric storm.

00:03:05.509 --> 00:03:05.519
As

00:03:05.519 --> 00:03:09.430
I

00:03:09.430 --> 00:03:09.440
looked

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:13.670
across the town,

00:03:13.670 --> 00:03:13.680
I

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:16.630
saw

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:19.430
fires burning in many buildings—nearly all

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:23.110
of them.

00:03:23.110 --> 00:03:23.120
Everyone

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:25.190
was

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:27.030
looting

00:03:27.030 --> 00:03:27.040
and

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:28.630
stealing,

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:31.589
acting godless. I want to interject

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:33.670
something:

00:03:42.599 --> 00:03:46.710
every person, even the greatest sinner, wakes up with a

00:03:46.720 --> 00:03:49.270
sense of peace they don't realize

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:50.190
they

00:03:50.200 --> 00:03:53.430
have.

00:03:56.470 --> 00:03:56.480
I

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:01.190
call this the prayer

00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:03.270
covering of the church. There

00:04:03.270 --> 00:04:03.280
is

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:07.670
a covering from

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:10.710
the praying people of

00:04:10.710 --> 00:04:10.720
the church

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:13.390
that covers the whole world,

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:15.150
bringing

00:04:15.160 --> 00:04:18.390
an atmosphere of

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:21.990
peace

00:04:21.990 --> 00:04:22.000
and

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:24.629
comfort that people don't realize

00:04:24.629 --> 00:04:24.639
is

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:27.030
there.

00:04:27.030 --> 00:04:27.040
When

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:29.749
the rapture of

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:32.790
the church takes place, that prayer

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:35.870
covering is removed for the first time.

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:38.950
There is total anarchy

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:43.749
because people feel the void

00:04:43.749 --> 00:04:43.759
where

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:47.270
that peace was, and they are freaking out. I

00:04:47.270 --> 00:04:47.280
felt that

00:04:47.280 --> 00:04:48.510
so

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:51.990
strongly

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:55.749
in the atmosphere;

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:58.310
it was

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:01.430
eerie and scary.

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:06.790
Suddenly,

00:05:09.960 --> 00:05:13.270
I was taken to

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:17.749
another scene. Jesus and I were

00:05:17.749 --> 00:05:17.759
suddenly

00:05:17.759 --> 00:05:20.390
in

00:05:20.390 --> 00:05:20.400
Berlin. I

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:23.550
saw

00:05:23.550 --> 00:05:23.560
a

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:28.310
man dressed in an expensive gray suit, a white

00:05:28.310 --> 00:05:28.320
shirt, and

00:05:28.320 --> 00:05:31.749
a nice tie

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:37.990
getting

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:41.830
out of a

00:05:41.830 --> 00:05:41.840
presidential-style

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:44.469
limousine.

00:05:44.479 --> 00:05:47.749
He was

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:50.629
driven to

00:05:57.600 --> 00:06:01.029
a massive conference

00:06:01.039 --> 00:06:03.309
room in

00:06:03.319 --> 00:06:06.950
Berlin

00:06:06.950 --> 00:06:06.960
where

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:09.189
people

00:06:09.199 --> 00:06:11.590
from all the nations of the

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.830
world were

00:06:13.830 --> 00:06:13.840
gathering

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:15.749
at a

00:06:15.749 --> 00:06:15.759
large

00:06:15.759 --> 00:06:18.629
round

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:21.510
table. He

00:06:21.510 --> 00:06:21.520
sat

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:24.550
at the

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:24.560
head.

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:27.550
I could not see his

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:30.710
face because the Lord

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:34.309
had

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:36.390
blotted it out, but I could see his

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:43.909
confident stature

00:06:43.909 --> 00:06:43.919
as

00:06:43.919 --> 00:06:47.510
the leaders listened to his plan. This occurred shortly after

00:06:47.510 --> 00:06:47.520
the rapture, perhaps within a few hours. Everyone listened

00:06:47.520 --> 00:06:50.870
to him because he

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:03.909
possessed

00:07:16.759 --> 00:07:19.670
a sense of

00:07:19.680 --> 00:07:21.830
confidence and peace similar

00:07:21.830 --> 00:07:21.840
to what

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:23.510
the church used to

00:07:23.510 --> 00:07:23.520
provide.

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:26.629
His

00:07:26.629 --> 00:07:26.639
presence

00:07:26.639 --> 00:07:29.270
brought

00:07:29.270 --> 00:07:29.280
a

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:31.670
sense of

00:07:31.670 --> 00:07:31.680
calm

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:33.710
that

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:38.950
made

00:07:38.950 --> 00:07:38.960
everyone

00:07:38.960 --> 00:07:41.189
want

00:07:41.199 --> 00:07:42.870
to listen. Their

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:44.629
eyes were fixed on him

00:07:44.639 --> 00:07:46.309
as

00:07:46.319 --> 00:07:50.870
he proposed a plan for

00:07:50.870 --> 00:07:50.880
a one-world

00:07:50.880 --> 00:07:51.950
currency and

00:07:51.950 --> 00:07:51.960
a

00:07:51.960 --> 00:07:57.110
chip.

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:16.350
Every world

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:20.950
leader surrendered their power to him

00:08:20.950 --> 00:08:20.960
during that

00:08:20.960 --> 00:08:23.309
single meeting.

00:08:23.309 --> 00:08:23.319
Then

00:08:23.319 --> 00:08:26.749
I was taken back to the courthouse.

00:08:28.599 --> 00:08:32.149
There was a

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:34.070
mandate, shown

00:08:34.070 --> 00:08:34.080
on

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:37.110
TVs everywhere,

00:08:37.110 --> 00:08:37.120
for

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:39.750
people

00:08:46.760 --> 00:08:51.910
to bring all Bibles

00:08:51.910 --> 00:08:51.920
to

00:08:51.920 --> 00:08:55.110
public places like

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:59.110
police stations or town

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:02.150
squares

00:09:02.160 --> 00:09:05.190
because owning one

00:09:05.190 --> 00:09:05.200
was no longer

00:09:05.200 --> 00:09:07.030
allowed.

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:12.790
They told

00:09:12.800 --> 00:09:14.670
people they could check out

00:09:14.670 --> 00:09:14.680
their

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:17.430
Bibles

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:19.190
later,

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:25.670
but anyone who did

00:09:25.670 --> 00:09:25.680
was

00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:27.590
marked

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:29.829
as

00:09:29.839 --> 00:09:32.389
a

00:09:32.399 --> 00:09:35.030
rebel.

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:36.470
Eventually,

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:39.670
they took the Bibles

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:43.350
and burned them. I saw massive

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:48.230
mounds of Bibles burning everywhere,

00:09:48.230 --> 00:09:48.240
creating

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:51.030
huge

00:09:51.030 --> 00:09:51.040
smokestacks.

00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:54.070
This

00:09:54.070 --> 00:09:54.080
was

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:56.389
happening

00:09:56.389 --> 00:09:56.399
in

00:09:56.399 --> 00:09:58.790
towns

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:01.110
all around the world.

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:05.829
It was

00:10:05.839 --> 00:10:07.910
against the law

00:10:07.910 --> 00:10:07.920
to

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:12.949
have a Bible. Then I saw him

00:10:12.959 --> 00:10:16.470
take down city,

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:20.310
state,

00:10:20.310 --> 00:10:20.320
and

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:23.590
American flags and replace them with his own.

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:26.150
And he put them on every

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:29.710
courthouse over all the major public

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:32.150
buildings that we would see an American

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:34.710
flag, or wherever you are,

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:36.710
your country flag, the French

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:40.069
flag, the German flag, or the

00:10:40.079 --> 00:10:41.990
United Kingdom flag. They

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:45.750
took those flags down and they put

00:10:45.760 --> 00:10:49.509
his flag up. And I'm going to show you

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:51.990
right now what that flag looks like. I

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:54.870
remember every bit of this

00:10:54.870 --> 00:10:54.880
clearly

00:10:54.880 --> 00:10:56.870
back from 2014 whenever the Lord

00:10:56.880 --> 00:10:59.509
showed me all this, what that flag looks

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:03.269
like. And it's two swords with

00:11:03.279 --> 00:11:06.310
palm branches

00:11:06.320 --> 00:11:09.230
on the top of it, and they're

00:11:09.240 --> 00:11:12.389
golden, and there's like a globe in the

00:11:12.399 --> 00:11:16.350
middle, and there was black, white, and

00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:19.670
green, and it represented

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:26.030
ISIS, al-Qaeda, and Hamas.

00:11:26.040 --> 00:11:28.590
All these terrorist

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:31.750
organizations were bringing forth what

00:11:31.760 --> 00:11:33.829
they called—now I will tell you the

00:11:33.839 --> 00:11:35.670
name of what everybody called him—the

00:11:35.670 --> 00:11:35.680
Mahdi.

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:38.310
I hope I don't butcher that,

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:40.230
but that's what they called

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:43.670
him. And everybody called this man the

00:11:43.670 --> 00:11:43.680
Mahdi.

00:11:43.680 --> 00:11:47.870
And

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:52.550
every time you see

00:11:52.550 --> 00:11:52.560
him—look,

00:11:52.560 --> 00:11:54.470
I don't want to skip around

00:11:54.480 --> 00:11:56.470
here too much—but they put the flag up

00:11:56.480 --> 00:11:59.110
like I'm saying, and it was honor to

00:11:59.120 --> 00:12:02.870
him, the

00:12:02.870 --> 00:12:02.880
Mahdi,

00:12:02.880 --> 00:12:08.030
bringing him into power.

00:12:08.040 --> 00:12:11.550
Now I see

00:12:11.560 --> 00:12:17.550
public squares with big huge movie

00:12:17.560 --> 00:12:22.310
screens, massive movie screens that are

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:26.910
as big as a huge building. But on

00:12:26.920 --> 00:12:30.590
Fridays, everybody dresses in white

00:12:30.600 --> 00:12:33.790
garments. They dress in like white

00:12:33.800 --> 00:12:38.990
robes by law. You go and on

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:41.870
Fridays they have

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:45.030
lines. All the people are in lines and

00:12:45.040 --> 00:12:49.590
they worship him on Fridays with

00:12:49.600 --> 00:12:51.590
the screen.

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:55.509
Some of it's live playback and some of

00:12:55.519 --> 00:12:58.629
it is pre-recorded because you can't

00:12:58.639 --> 00:13:00.710
worship all around the world in the

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:02.629
daytime because it's not daytime

00:13:02.639 --> 00:13:06.389
everywhere. But they were taken, and even

00:13:06.389 --> 00:13:06.399
where—I

00:13:06.399 --> 00:13:09.030
know I

00:13:09.040 --> 00:13:12.069
told you all in a previous video,

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:14.310
if you go look at some of my stuff

00:13:14.310 --> 00:13:14.320
before—where

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:17.350
they worship,

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:21.430
and it's at a big Mason temple. It's

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:24.710
at a huge Freemason's

00:13:24.720 --> 00:13:27.590
temple. They have huge white screens all

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:30.470
on the front of this building

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:32.069
and this is where the people

00:13:32.079 --> 00:13:33.949
come on Fridays to worship the

00:13:33.959 --> 00:13:36.629
antichrist. They're in single file

00:13:36.639 --> 00:13:38.310
lines and they all gather in these

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:39.910
fields. Now, fill in the field—it goes

00:13:39.920 --> 00:13:42.470
way back there and it goes all the way

00:13:42.480 --> 00:13:44.150
around the building, the whole building.

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:46.069
And this is where all the

00:13:46.069 --> 00:13:46.079
townspeople

00:13:46.079 --> 00:13:48.389
from all the major towns come and they

00:13:48.399 --> 00:13:49.990
start worshiping the antichrist.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:52.629
I saw him worshiping

00:13:52.639 --> 00:13:55.750
in Rome at the

00:13:55.750 --> 00:13:55.760
place

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:59.110
where the Catholics worship, by where

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:03.990
the pope is, that square,

00:14:06.880 --> 00:14:09.030
the Catholic church and

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:11.110
the Vatican.

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:13.990
They have major

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:16.150
screens there. They have major screens

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:19.430
in Europe and in Paris. It's everywhere.

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:21.750
Even at

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:27.189
Buckingham Palace,

00:14:27.199 --> 00:14:28.870
they had them there. I'm

00:14:28.880 --> 00:14:31.069
telling you, they're

