00:28:30.120 --> 00:28:32.789
the Christians running as fast as

00:28:32.799 --> 00:28:34.870
they could

00:28:36.640 --> 00:28:37.909
to grab

00:28:37.919 --> 00:28:40.149
corn, vegetables, or

00:28:41.919 --> 00:28:44.149
chickens

00:28:44.159 --> 00:28:47.590
to try to get food. Whenever someone would

00:28:49.760 --> 00:28:51.750
see these people

00:28:51.760 --> 00:28:53.909
running and call it

00:28:53.909 --> 00:28:53.919
in,

00:28:53.919 --> 00:28:56.950
I saw them putting blocks

00:28:56.960 --> 00:29:00.310
in the roads—massive barricades. The

00:29:00.320 --> 00:29:02.950
Christians would use things to spike

00:29:02.960 --> 00:29:05.669
the tires of these people.

00:29:05.669 --> 00:29:05.679
They

00:29:05.679 --> 00:29:07.430
were

00:29:07.440 --> 00:29:10.310
in black Hummers

00:29:10.320 --> 00:29:13.830
with blue lights. I saw these massive

00:29:13.840 --> 00:29:17.190
army tank-like cars with

00:29:17.200 --> 00:29:20.310
men in solid black outfits

00:29:20.310 --> 00:29:20.320
and

00:29:20.320 --> 00:29:23.510
black shields over their faces.

00:29:29.520 --> 00:29:31.269
They would drive up in these

00:29:31.269 --> 00:29:31.279
Hummer-like

00:29:31.279 --> 00:29:33.669
cars with blue

00:29:33.679 --> 00:29:36.630
lights in them; they

00:29:36.630 --> 00:29:36.640
were

00:29:36.640 --> 00:29:39.590
almost like black

00:29:39.600 --> 00:29:42.310
lights.

00:29:42.320 --> 00:29:45.269
I remember them

00:29:45.279 --> 00:29:47.269
jumping out and the Christians

00:29:47.279 --> 00:29:49.190
running as fast as they could to

00:29:49.200 --> 00:29:52.310
get away. The men jumped

00:29:52.320 --> 00:29:55.230
out with

00:29:55.240 --> 00:29:58.789
guns that I've never seen before.

00:29:58.799 --> 00:30:00.549
I've told people about this and

00:30:00.559 --> 00:30:02.470
they said they actually exist—there

00:30:02.470 --> 00:30:02.480
are

00:30:02.480 --> 00:30:03.909
prototypes.

00:30:03.909 --> 00:30:03.919
They

00:30:03.919 --> 00:30:06.310
pulled the

00:30:06.320 --> 00:30:08.710
trigger and it was like a pulse,

00:30:08.720 --> 00:30:11.830
some kind

00:30:11.840 --> 00:30:15.230
of riot control that knocked you out

00:30:15.240 --> 00:30:17.430
for a couple of

00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:20.549
minutes. They just pointed it

00:30:20.549 --> 00:30:20.559
in a

00:30:20.559 --> 00:30:22.710
direction,

00:30:22.720 --> 00:30:25.590
and as soon as that beam

00:30:25.600 --> 00:30:28.470
hit

00:30:28.480 --> 00:30:30.750
that individual, it knocked them

00:30:30.760 --> 00:30:33.230
unconscious. There was no running

00:30:33.240 --> 00:30:36.470
away. It was on the Hummers

00:30:36.470 --> 00:30:36.480
and

00:30:36.480 --> 00:30:39.190
on the men, and

00:30:39.200 --> 00:30:41.190
they would just scan the people as they

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:42.549
were running. The people would just

00:30:42.559 --> 00:30:44.310
fall out as if

00:30:44.310 --> 00:30:44.320
they were

00:30:44.320 --> 00:30:46.389
passing out, but it

00:30:46.399 --> 00:30:49.430
didn't kill them.

00:30:52.600 --> 00:30:56.149
Then the men would walk up on

00:30:56.159 --> 00:30:59.669
them and tell them,

00:30:59.679 --> 00:31:01.990
'Take the mark or we're going to cut your

00:31:02.000 --> 00:31:03.750
head

00:31:03.750 --> 00:31:03.760
off.'So

00:31:03.760 --> 00:31:08.630
I saw a woman and her two children

00:31:08.640 --> 00:31:11.230
that were born during the

00:31:11.240 --> 00:31:15.029
tribulation and her husband all

00:31:15.039 --> 00:31:17.669
standing there like this. They told

00:31:17.679 --> 00:31:20.630
the mother, 'If you don't take the mark

00:31:20.640 --> 00:31:23.029
and the children don't take the mark,

00:31:23.039 --> 00:31:24.950
we're going to cut those children's heads

00:31:24.950 --> 00:31:24.960
off.'And

00:31:24.960 --> 00:31:28.389
as any mother that's good

00:31:28.399 --> 00:31:31.190
would say, she was

00:31:31.200 --> 00:31:33.909
freaking out. 'Don't cut my

00:31:33.909 --> 00:31:33.919
babies'heads

00:31:33.919 --> 00:31:38.630
off! I'll take the mark.'And I saw her,

00:31:38.640 --> 00:31:41.509
right before my face, take the mark of

00:31:41.519 --> 00:31:44.149
the beast. And the children took the

00:31:44.159 --> 00:31:46.710
mark of the beast. And the

00:31:46.720 --> 00:31:49.990
father said, 'No, I'll never take the

00:31:50.000 --> 00:31:53.310
mark of the beast.'And I saw those

00:31:53.320 --> 00:31:56.630
men; they pulled his head out

00:31:56.640 --> 00:32:01.110
and they had a massive sword,

00:32:01.120 --> 00:32:03.750
and they chopped his head off right

00:32:03.760 --> 00:32:08.149
before me. And I saw his head roll right

00:32:08.159 --> 00:32:11.269
before my feet. They couldn't see me,

00:32:11.279 --> 00:32:14.389
and they could not see Jesus, but

00:32:14.399 --> 00:32:16.950
Jesus told me to look. And this is

00:32:16.960 --> 00:32:19.190
something interesting: the whole time

00:32:19.200 --> 00:32:22.070
Jesus never had to speak out loud

00:32:22.080 --> 00:32:25.509
verbally to me. I could hear what he was

00:32:25.519 --> 00:32:26.990
saying

00:32:27.000 --> 00:32:30.389
by his thoughts, and he could hear

00:32:30.399 --> 00:32:33.029
what I was saying by my thoughts. I just

00:32:33.039 --> 00:32:35.110
knew it was like

00:32:35.120 --> 00:32:36.710
I was out of my body. I don't know;

00:32:36.720 --> 00:32:38.750
it was way out there, what

00:32:38.760 --> 00:32:41.990
happened. But I could smell

00:32:42.000 --> 00:32:45.269
the blood from the man that got his head

00:32:45.279 --> 00:32:48.630
cut off right before me. And the

00:32:48.640 --> 00:32:52.110
kids and the mother had no

00:32:52.120 --> 00:32:56.269
expression. The chip makes you

00:32:56.279 --> 00:33:00.149
motionless, having no emotions at all. You

00:33:00.159 --> 00:33:04.789
become like a zombie. It makes your mind

00:33:04.799 --> 00:33:05.789
instantaneously

00:33:05.799 --> 00:33:08.549
like a zombie. It's like,

00:33:08.559 --> 00:33:11.190
'Hello, there's nothing

00:33:11.190 --> 00:33:11.200
there.'The

00:33:11.200 --> 00:33:14.389
children did not cry or wail or

00:33:14.399 --> 00:33:18.070
anything at all upset because

00:33:18.080 --> 00:33:20.470
their father just got his head cut off.

00:33:20.480 --> 00:33:22.389
And the wife didn't even act like she

00:33:22.399 --> 00:33:24.070
cared either. It was like she

00:33:24.080 --> 00:33:28.190
was not there.

00:33:28.200 --> 00:33:31.509
So, he's dead. The wife and the children

00:33:31.519 --> 00:33:34.230
are okay. They have the chip now, but

00:33:34.240 --> 00:33:36.149
they're damned to hell forever because

00:33:36.159 --> 00:33:38.389
of what happened. Now, are the children

00:33:38.399 --> 00:33:40.630
damned to hell forever? I don't

00:33:40.640 --> 00:33:43.190
believe that. There's no way. In my

00:33:43.200 --> 00:33:45.909
heart, I'm just going to say the

00:33:45.919 --> 00:33:48.310
children didn't choose it. They were

00:33:48.320 --> 00:33:50.870
forced; it was forced on them. And

00:33:50.880 --> 00:33:53.990
God's a merciful God when it

00:33:54.000 --> 00:33:56.070
comes to kids. So, I'm not going

00:33:56.080 --> 00:33:59.269
to sit here and get in a theological

00:33:59.279 --> 00:34:01.909
debate about it. I'm just telling you

00:34:01.919 --> 00:34:04.389
the kids didn't choose to take it. It

00:34:04.399 --> 00:34:06.710
was forced on them. And so,

00:34:06.720 --> 00:34:08.629
I just know God's a merciful God.

00:34:08.639 --> 00:34:10.470
Now, I don't know the condition of their soul. I know what

00:34:12.240 --> 00:34:13.909
the

00:34:13.919 --> 00:34:16.470
Bible says, that anybody who takes the mark

00:34:16.480 --> 00:34:18.629
goes to hell and they burn forever and

00:34:18.639 --> 00:34:21.109
ever. But if it was forced on

00:34:21.119 --> 00:34:22.869
you, you didn't accept it. You have to

00:34:22.879 --> 00:34:26.389
actually accept this. So, I'm just

00:34:26.399 --> 00:34:28.230
going to leave that there. You do with

00:34:28.240 --> 00:34:30.550
it what you want to, but don't

00:34:30.560 --> 00:34:34.589
criticize me in the comments.

00:34:34.599 --> 00:34:39.750
So, now I'm going to go to this. I saw

00:34:39.760 --> 00:34:44.149
in every single town, on the major

00:34:44.159 --> 00:34:46.790
highways or the roads coming into the

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:50.589
town, they had barricades like

00:34:50.599 --> 00:34:53.349
checkpoints that everybody had to go

00:34:53.359 --> 00:34:56.869
through to come in or out of that town.

00:34:56.879 --> 00:34:59.510
And the only way you were allowed in

00:34:59.520 --> 00:35:03.030
those major cities or towns was by the

00:35:03.040 --> 00:35:05.589
mark of the beast. They scanned

00:35:05.599 --> 00:35:09.270
your hand or your forehead to get inside

00:35:09.280 --> 00:35:12.550
there to get supplies like groceries,

00:35:12.560 --> 00:35:15.750
medical, or to go to the doctor,

00:35:15.760 --> 00:35:18.150
whatever you had to do. You had to go

00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:20.230
through those major

00:35:20.240 --> 00:35:22.870
army checkpoints with these men in these

00:35:22.880 --> 00:35:25.589
black outfits. They scanned you. And I

00:35:25.599 --> 00:35:27.510
saw people on foot trying to go in

00:35:27.520 --> 00:35:29.430
there. And this is another thing: I

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:35.349
saw

00:35:35.359 --> 00:35:38.390
that

00:35:38.400 --> 00:35:40.910
some of the people got a

00:35:40.920 --> 00:35:43.829
sore on their hand or their forehead

00:35:43.839 --> 00:35:47.589
that looked like a massive infection.

00:35:47.599 --> 00:35:51.190
It looked like a boil

00:35:51.200 --> 00:35:53.829
on their forehead or their

00:35:53.839 --> 00:35:56.790
hand that had a bruise. It

00:35:56.800 --> 00:35:59.190
looked like an infection. It had pus on

00:35:59.200 --> 00:36:03.270
it. It looked very, very painful. And I

00:36:03.280 --> 00:36:06.950
saw a woman that was

00:36:06.960 --> 00:36:10.390
standing in line who had put makeup

00:36:10.400 --> 00:36:14.470
on her hand and was trying to imitate

00:36:14.480 --> 00:36:18.470
the mark of the beast sore.

00:36:18.480 --> 00:36:21.550
She was that desperate to get into that

00:36:21.560 --> 00:36:24.950
town for food or medical supplies or

00:36:24.960 --> 00:36:27.829
whatever she needed. She was

00:36:27.839 --> 00:36:30.150
just trying to fake it. And so, when

00:36:30.160 --> 00:36:33.510
they saw that she was faking it, when

00:36:33.520 --> 00:36:35.589
they got up there to scan her hand,

00:36:35.599 --> 00:36:37.750
there was no mercy. They cut her head

00:36:37.760 --> 00:36:40.069
off right there. They killed her right

00:36:40.079 --> 00:36:42.069
there. They just

00:36:42.079 --> 00:36:43.510
cut her head off and it just rolled down

00:36:43.520 --> 00:36:46.790
the street and nobody cared.

00:36:46.800 --> 00:36:48.870
All the other people in line, like I

00:36:48.880 --> 00:36:51.589
said, are zombies.

00:36:51.599 --> 00:36:53.349
They were all standing in

00:36:53.359 --> 00:36:55.910
line; I saw it all. And they would go

00:36:55.920 --> 00:36:57.430
through these

00:36:57.440 --> 00:37:00.790
checkpoints to get

00:37:00.800 --> 00:37:02.630
groceries or whatever from coming in

00:37:02.630 --> 00:37:02.640
and

00:37:02.640 --> 00:37:05.470
out of the city.

00:37:05.480 --> 00:37:08.390
And like I said, the drones are

00:37:08.400 --> 00:37:10.790
always flying. The drones are always

00:37:10.800 --> 00:37:12.870
scanning people. The drones are always

00:37:12.880 --> 00:37:14.710
alerting the authorities if you're

00:37:14.720 --> 00:37:16.390
shooting guns or whatever, trying to get

00:37:16.400 --> 00:37:18.390
food or rabbits, trying to

00:37:18.400 --> 00:37:20.870
stay alive, and

00:37:20.880 --> 00:37:23.510
stealing from the farmers.

00:37:23.520 --> 00:37:28.470
I saw a man mowing

00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:31.670
his grass with no expression on his

00:37:31.680 --> 00:37:34.870
face. He was mowing his grass, but he

00:37:34.880 --> 00:37:37.589
was gone. It was the weirdest

00:37:37.599 --> 00:37:39.349
thing seeing these people that took the

00:37:39.359 --> 00:37:41.430
mark of the beast. They were

00:37:41.440 --> 00:37:43.750
just wiped out.

00:37:43.760 --> 00:37:45.349
He was mowing, but he had

00:37:45.359 --> 00:37:49.109
no expression. Then I saw a man trying

00:37:49.119 --> 00:37:52.790
to commit suicide,

00:37:52.800 --> 00:37:55.990
trying to jump off of a bridge. But

00:37:56.000 --> 00:38:00.310
whenever he did, it created peace in his

00:38:00.320 --> 00:38:04.069
mind. The chip sent a signal to

00:38:04.079 --> 00:38:04.910
his

00:38:04.920 --> 00:38:09.030
mind because it knew that hormone or

00:38:09.040 --> 00:38:11.510
that thought pattern or whatever

00:38:11.520 --> 00:38:13.510
your body creates when you're

00:38:13.510 --> 00:38:13.520
about

00:38:13.520 --> 00:38:16.069
to do something like that. It

00:38:16.079 --> 00:38:19.030
knew by your heart rate or whatever to

00:38:19.040 --> 00:38:21.910
calm you down. So he was standing there

00:38:21.920 --> 00:38:24.630
ready to jump off this major bridge to

00:38:24.640 --> 00:38:28.310
end himself and all of a

00:38:28.320 --> 00:38:30.550
sudden that chip caused him to calm down

00:38:30.560 --> 00:38:31.990
and he just stepped down and walked back.

00:38:32.000 --> 00:38:33.910
So there was

00:38:33.920 --> 00:38:36.230
no way to even do anything physically to

00:38:36.240 --> 00:38:39.510
yourself. It

00:38:39.520 --> 00:38:42.470
would not allow you

00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:45.190
to. You didn't have free will anymore.

00:38:45.200 --> 00:38:46.950
If you were trying to do anything

00:38:46.960 --> 00:38:50.150
like riot or steal,

00:38:50.160 --> 00:38:54.710
your mind would not do that.

00:38:54.720 --> 00:38:57.910
It made peace over

00:38:57.920 --> 00:39:01.990
you.

00:39:03.720 --> 00:39:06.950
I don't know how it did it, but

00:39:06.960 --> 00:39:08.630
I'm just telling you all it was the

00:39:08.640 --> 00:39:10.230
weirdest thing I've ever seen. And it

00:39:10.240 --> 00:39:12.550
happened to everybody who took it. Now,

00:39:12.560 --> 00:39:15.510
I was taken to Israel and I see the

00:39:15.520 --> 00:39:18.230
temple and the stone

00:39:18.240 --> 00:39:20.790
columns and I see the third temple

00:39:20.800 --> 00:39:23.349
that's going to be built soon.

00:39:23.359 --> 00:39:26.230
It's beautiful. The stone columns,

00:39:26.240 --> 00:39:28.710
the scrolling, all of it. It's

00:39:28.720 --> 00:39:30.790
gorgeous the way it's all done, but it's

00:39:30.800 --> 00:39:34.390
built up. He has a white thing on his

00:39:34.400 --> 00:39:36.550
head. And I'm going to say this.

00:39:36.560 --> 00:39:38.230
My son's helping me with this because

00:39:38.240 --> 00:39:40.790
it's a lot to remember, but he

00:39:40.800 --> 00:39:45.190
had salt-and-pepper on his beard. It

00:39:45.200 --> 00:39:47.829
looked like time had passed,

00:39:47.839 --> 00:39:50.069
but something happened to his beard

00:39:50.079 --> 00:39:52.630
where it wasn't all black anymore.

00:39:52.640 --> 00:39:54.870
Before it looked kind of

00:39:54.870 --> 00:39:54.880
clean-shaven,

00:39:54.880 --> 00:39:57.990
but it wasn't really long

00:39:58.000 --> 00:40:00.790
like this was. It was

00:40:06.240 --> 00:40:08.790
thicker and it looked

00:40:08.800 --> 00:40:11.190
like it had salt and pepper in it in his

00:40:11.200 --> 00:40:16.230
hairline right here too. So, I

00:40:16.240 --> 00:40:18.310
believe it was a certain man

00:40:18.320 --> 00:40:20.750
that's in Saudi Arabia. On this side of

00:40:20.760 --> 00:40:25.270
him, I believe I saw the pope.

00:40:25.280 --> 00:40:27.349
Please don't throw eggs at me; I'm just

00:40:27.359 --> 00:40:29.109
telling you what I felt like I saw.

00:40:29.119 --> 00:40:32.390
It looked like the pope. This man

00:40:32.400 --> 00:40:34.710
over here because he was dressed in all

00:40:34.720 --> 00:40:36.390
white like that and it had that little

00:40:36.400 --> 00:40:40.790
thing on his head. And

00:40:40.800 --> 00:40:43.829
this man over here was another spiritual

00:40:43.839 --> 00:40:46.790
leader. So, they were and I believe that

00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:50.870
is Noah. He's a man over

00:40:50.870 --> 00:40:50.880
there—it

00:40:50.880 --> 00:40:53.990
doesn't matter.

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:55.349
Do you all want to look at it? His name

00:40:55.359 --> 00:40:58.230
is Noah, but I believe he was

00:40:58.240 --> 00:41:01.109
on this side of him. He

00:41:01.119 --> 00:41:03.829
was standing; they had these two men and

00:41:03.839 --> 00:41:06.390
him and they were all talking. He was

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:08.069
talking, and whenever he started

00:41:08.079 --> 00:41:10.150
professing that he was Lord, I saw

00:41:10.160 --> 00:41:14.349
lightning striking above his

00:41:14.359 --> 00:41:16.790
head. This was one of the last

00:41:16.800 --> 00:41:19.109
things I saw before the Lord took me

00:41:19.109 --> 00:41:19.119
to

00:41:19.119 --> 00:41:22.390
the edge of heaven and the earth. I

00:41:22.390 --> 00:41:22.400
saw

00:41:22.400 --> 00:41:24.230
all this stuff going

00:41:24.230 --> 00:41:24.240
on—there

00:41:24.240 --> 00:41:26.230
was lightning, I saw people, and

00:41:26.240 --> 00:41:29.109
he was professing that he was God.

00:41:29.109 --> 00:41:29.119
Suddenly,

00:41:29.119 --> 00:41:30.950
Jesus and I took off and

00:41:30.960 --> 00:41:34.430
went up to heaven. He showed

00:41:34.440 --> 00:41:37.390
me a

00:41:37.400 --> 00:41:42.270
massive world

00:41:42.280 --> 00:41:46.309
as far as the eye could see. He said,

00:41:46.319 --> 00:41:48.550
"This is the revival that's about to take

00:41:48.560 --> 00:41:52.510
place."I

00:41:52.520 --> 00:41:55.910
could see tears in his eyes; he

00:41:55.920 --> 00:41:58.910
wasn't crying, but his eyes filled with

00:41:58.920 --> 00:42:03.349
tears. He looked at China,

00:42:03.359 --> 00:42:05.750
pointed down, and said,

00:42:05.760 --> 00:42:07.589
"Brandon, do you see all those little

00:42:07.589 --> 00:42:07.599
lights?"because

00:42:07.599 --> 00:42:09.670
there

00:42:09.680 --> 00:42:11.190
were

00:42:11.200 --> 00:42:13.670
lights. They were all over the

00:42:13.680 --> 00:42:17.510
globe, all over the map.

00:42:17.520 --> 00:42:20.309
There were all kinds of what looked like

00:42:20.319 --> 00:42:22.510
little torches,

00:42:22.520 --> 00:42:25.750
